{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T08:51:42.720Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Long-running agent execution model"},{"type":"text","text":" in the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude Managed Agents Platform"},{"type":"text","text":" is the architectural pattern where Claude runs as an autonomous agent in a managed cloud or self-hosted sandbox for "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"minutes or hours"},{"type":"text","text":", executing many tool calls in a continuous, stateful session instead of a single prompt-response turn. Managed Agents provides the harness and infrastructure so your application doesn't need to build its own agent loop, sandbox, or tool-execution layer; you just define the agent and start sessions."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The long-running execution model means:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"One session"},{"type":"text","text":" is a running agent instance that persists filesystem state, tool history, and conversation history server-side.\n- Claude autonomously "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"plans"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"executes tools"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"reads results"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"continues working"},{"type":"text","text":" until the task is done or interrupted.\n- Your application can "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"stream responses"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"send steering events"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"interrupt"},{"type":"text","text":" the agent mid-execution without losing progress.\n- Sessions are "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"stateful by design"},{"type":"text","text":": they resume cleanly after pauses and store everything server-side."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This contrasts with typical chat-style prompting where each request is short, stateless, and limited to a single turn. Long-running execution is intended for multi-step, long-horizon tasks that require multiple tool calls and intermediate reasoning."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Long-running execution solves the core problem of AI agent reliability on complex tasks: instead of trying to force a single massive response, Claude can "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"pause in place with full execution state intact"},{"type":"text","text":"—reasoning chain, working memory, tool history, and pending work—then continue when more context or time is available."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For production workloads, this means:\n- Tasks that take "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"minutes or hours"},{"type":"text","text":" can run without your own orchestration code.\n- You get "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"cloud sandboxes"},{"type":"text","text":" with pre-installed packages and network access, or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"self-hosted sandboxes"},{"type":"text","text":" for compliance.\n- You don't need to build your own "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"agent loop"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"sandbox"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"tool execution layer"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of it as a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"managed runtime"},{"type":"text","text":" for Claude agents, not a chat API. You define:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Agent"},{"type":"text","text":": the model, system prompt, tools, MCP servers, and skills.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Environment"},{"type":"text","text":": where sessions run (Anthropic-managed cloud sandbox or your own infrastructure).\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Session"},{"type":"text","text":": a running agent instance in that environment, performing a specific task.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Events"},{"type":"text","text":": messages exchanged between your application and the agent (user turns, tool results, status updates)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The agent loop is handled by Managed Agents infrastructure; your code sends events and streams back results."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How it works"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The platform follows a five-step flow:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Create an agent"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Define the model, system prompt, tools, MCP servers, and skills. Create the agent once and reference it by ID across sessions."}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Create an environment"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure where the agent runs: an Anthropic-managed cloud sandbox, or a self-hosted sandbox on your infrastructure."}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Start a session"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Launch a session that references your agent and environment configuration."}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Send events and stream responses"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Send user messages as events. Claude autonomously executes tools and streams back results through server-sent events (SSE). Event history is persisted server-side and can be fetched in full."}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Steer or interrupt"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Send additional user events to guide the agent mid-execution, or interrupt it to change direction."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the core long-running pattern: a single session that persists and can be steered over time, rather than a series of independent API calls."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Stateful sessions"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sessions are "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"long-running and stateful"},{"type":"text","text":" by design:\n- They run for "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"minutes or hours"},{"type":"text","text":" with multiple tool calls.\n- They "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"resume cleanly after pauses"},{"type":"text","text":".\n- They store "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"conversation history"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"sandbox state"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"outputs server-side"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Because sessions persist state server-side, Managed Agents is not eligible for Zero Data Retention or HIPAA BAA coverage. This is an architectural trade-off: statefulness for long-running work versus strict data-retention policies."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to use long-running execution"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The long-running model is best for workloads that need:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Long-running execution"},{"type":"text","text":": Tasks that run for minutes or hours with multiple tool calls\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cloud infrastructure"},{"type":"text","text":": Secure sandboxes with pre-installed packages and network access\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Self-hosted execution"},{"type":"text","text":": Sandboxes on infrastructure you control for compliance or data-residency requirements\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Minimal infrastructure"},{"type":"text","text":": No need to build your own agent loop, sandbox, or tool execution layer\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Stateful sessions"},{"type":"text","text":": Persistent filesystems and conversation history across multiple interactions"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key characteristics"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Aspect"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Long-running model"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Typical chat prompting"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Duration"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Minutes to hours"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Seconds"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tool calls"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Many, autonomous"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Limited or none"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"State"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Server-persisted session"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Stateless per request"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Orchestration"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Handled by Managed Agents"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Your code builds agent loop"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Interruptibility"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Can steer mid-execution"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each request is independent"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use case"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Complex, multi-step tasks"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Single-turn Q&A"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Practical example"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A typical long-running agent task might be:\n1. Start a session for a code-refactoring agent.\n2. Send an event: \"Refactor this Python module to use async I/O.\"\n3. Claude reads files, writes new code, runs tests, and iterates.\n4. You stream intermediate tool results and logs.\n5. At hour 1, you interrupt and add: \"Also add type hints to all functions.\"\n6. The session continues from the same state, with filesystem and history intact.\n7. When done, you fetch the full event history and final outputs."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pricing model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The platform charges standard Claude API token rates plus "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"$0.08 per session-hour of active runtime"},{"type":"text","text":". This reflects the long-running nature: you pay for the time the agent is actively executing in the sandbox, not just for tokens."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trade-offs"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- No custom agent loop or sandbox infrastructure.\n- Long-horizon tasks run reliably with state persistence.\n- Built-in prompt caching, compaction, and performance optimizations.\n- Streamed results and server-side event history."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Trade-offs:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Sessions persist data server-side, so you lose Zero Data Retention and HIPAA BAA eligibility.\n- You pay per session-hour in addition to token costs.\n- You're using a managed runtime rather than having full control over orchestration."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Long-running execution means "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"one persistent, stateful session"},{"type":"text","text":" that runs for minutes or hours with many tool calls."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Managed Agents provides the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"harness and infrastructure"},{"type":"text","text":"; you define the agent and start sessions."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sessions are "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"stateful by design"},{"type":"text","text":": they persist conversation history, sandbox state, and outputs server-side."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"steer or interrupt"},{"type":"text","text":" mid-execution without losing progress."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The model is best for "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"complex, multi-step tasks"},{"type":"text","text":" where you don't want to build your own agent loop."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}}
